<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11295</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，凯蒂和乔伊飞快地跑进教室。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们刚坐到椅子上，上课铃就响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂看了看右边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克在小声说话，奥利维亚在笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂翻了个白眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好，各位同学。” 贝柔老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拿出你们的铅笔和本子，我们开始学习。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是四年级的数学书！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44748</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡洛斯低头看了看课本封面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44749</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看见一个圆盘被等分成了八块。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道这个图片是什么意思！” 他嘟囔着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要学更多的分数！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天不学分数，卡洛斯。” 贝柔老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们要学整数——数值大的整数。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还要学习数十的倍数。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们也许能数到一百万！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>数学课后是科学课。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贝柔老师给每个学生发了一本叫做《两栖动物》的书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚指了指封面上的青蛙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这像是黑绿相间的箭毒蛙！它们住在夏威夷！” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真能装聪明。” 凯蒂想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 她哗哗地翻起了书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94906</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“乌龟在哪儿？” 凯蒂喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“三趾箱龟就住在我家后院。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听上去很有趣！” 贝柔老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109206</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，乌龟不是两栖动物，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂，乌龟是爬行动物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂的脸红了。“哎呀！” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>科学课后，贝柔老师宣布要做一个有关健康的发表活动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从现在开始，我们应该关注健康问题。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135747</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你能照顾好你自己，你就会拥有一个好心情，也会更长寿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135748</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贝柔老师给每个人发了一本叫做《健康管理》的书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“下个星期，大家都要到前边发表。” 老师接着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们要在这本书里选择一个主题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我希望你们能够充分发挥想象力，写出一份更有意思的发表。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她让每个学生从一个盒子里抽出一张纸条。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚是第一个，她打开了纸条。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170730</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“健康的皮肤。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>劳拉抽到了 “健康的眼睛” 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175262</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克抽到了 “营养” 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡洛斯打开了他的纸条。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“健康的耳朵。” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？我听不见你说什么。” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没人笑。她看了看四周。“明白了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“明白了。” 卡洛斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拉里抽到了 “安全运动” 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，有人抽到了 “睡眠与休息” 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203946</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下一个该凯蒂了，她把手伸进了盒子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“运动！” 凯蒂读着纸条，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿，这和 ‘玩儿’ 是一样的，不是吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贝柔老师笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，凯蒂，有些人也会那么认为。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，该乔伊了。“建立友谊？” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这也是和健康有关的主题吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。” 贝柔老师说，“朋友可以帮助我们相信自己。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这也是保持健康的一个重要部分。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的！” 乔伊说。她喜欢她的主题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>关于 “友谊” 的发表一定会很有趣的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天的课就上到这儿，同学们。” 贝柔老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请在铃响前把东西收拾好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，四年级的学生们就冲出了教学楼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天还不错。” 凯蒂对乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们俩的健康主题似乎都很有趣。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，凯蒂听见卢克用尖尖的声音喊道：“贝柔老师，乌龟在哪儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>除了凯蒂，所有的同学都大笑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那不好笑，卢克！” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有些同学想不笑，但他们没忍住。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288906</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他只是在开玩笑，凯蒂。” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288907</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别生气。” 卢克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂！我有一个好主意，我们都去 ‘脆皮派天堂’ 吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂还是很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299440</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“和你？不了，谢谢！” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她骑上自己的自行车，飞快地沿着校园马路骑走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“凯蒂肯定生气了。” 卡洛斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她是生气了。” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320544</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我从来没听说过脆皮派。” 奥利维亚说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320545</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么是脆皮派？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都露出了微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“脆皮派很甜！” 劳拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“脆皮派有水果味儿！” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“卢克妈妈做的脆皮派是全城最好吃的！” 卡洛斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>338047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>341232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们比赛吧！” 卢克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>341233</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>346654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“各就各位，预备，出发！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>